<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَشك يشك شكاًّ:</span> أَصَابَهُ ذَلِك.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">والكيكة:</span> الطَّرِيقَة.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">ودعه هلى شكيكته:</span> أَي طَرِيقَته.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَالْجمع:</span> شكائك، على الْقيَاس، وشكك، نادرة.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَرجل مُخْتَلف الشكة:</span> متفاوت الْأَخْلَاق.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَالشَّكّ:</span> الْحلَّة الَّتِي تلبس ظُهُور السيتين وضربوا بُيُوتهم شكاكاً: أَي صفا وَاحِدًا،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ ثَعْلَب:</span> إِنَّمَا هُوَ <span class="c1">" سكاك "</span> يشتقه من السِّكَّة،<span class="c5"> وَهُوَ:</span> الزقاق الْوَاسِع.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>الْكَاف وَالضَّاد<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>[<span class="c2">(ض ك ك)</span> و <span class="c2">(ض ك ض ك)</span>]<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>ضكه يضكه ضكاًّ،<span class="c5"> وضكضكه:</span> غمزه غمزا شَدِيدا وضغطه.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">وضكه بِالْحجَّةِ:</span> قهره.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وضكه الْأَمر:</span> كربه.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">والضك:</span> الضّيق.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">والضكضكة:</span> ضرب من الْمَشْي.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">وَقيل:</span> هِيَ السرعة.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>والضكضاك،<span class="c5"> والضكاضك من الرِّجَال:</span> الْقصير المكتنز.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">وَامْرَأَة ضكضاكة:</span> كَذَلِك.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>الْكَاف وَالصَّاد<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>[<span class="c2">(ك ص ص)</span> و <span class="c2">(ك ص ك ص)</span>]<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c5">الكصيص:</span> الصَّوْت، عَامَّة.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c5">وَقيل:</span> هُوَ الصَّوْت الرَّقِيق الضَّعِيف عِنْد الْفَزع وَنَحْوه.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c5">وَقيل:</span> هُوَ الْهَرَب.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c5">وَقيل:</span> الرعدة.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>